Class Prefix

java.lang.Object
  com.tailf.jnc.Attribute
      com.tailf.jnc.Prefix
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Prefix
extends Attribute
implements java.io.Serializable

This class represents a prefix mapping of a prefix string into a namespace. For example: 

    xmlns:foo='http://foo.com'

Provides a mapping from prefix "foo" into the namespace "http://foo.com".
